	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;This is approximately&lt;strong&gt; 150 million&lt;/strong&gt; kilometers or 93 million miles.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The distance between the Earth and the Moon is approximately&lt;strong&gt; 384,400 kilometers.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The distance between Jupiter and the Sun is approximately &lt;strong&gt;5.20 astronomical units.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The distance between Pluto and the Sun is approximately &lt;strong&gt;39.5 astronomical units.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
